descriptionHtml:
[color=khaki][size=6]Description[/size][/color]
Piercings are made for UNPB BBP 2.52 body
Piercings are craftable in jewellery, 5 types: with chains (tops and bottoms) and simple gems for top, navel, bottom
5 color variants of each (emerald, amber, ruby, sapphire, amethyst/ruby with copper)
You can make anything what you want while it is non-commercial destribution and you give me credits as original mod author.
I don't give permission to upload it in steam.
author: newmiller
